description: Ryder and the pups leave Adventure Bay to face their arch-rival, Mayor Humdinger, after he becomes the mayor of nearby Adventure City and wreaks havoc there. While one particular pup must face his past, the team finds help from a new member, the savvy dachshund Liberty. Together, armed with exciting new gadgets and gear, the PAW Patrol fights to save the citizens of Adventure City.
title: PAW Patrol: The Movie
